msgid "# Qwen3.5-Dense (Qwen3.5-2B/4B/9B)"
msgstr "# Qwen3.5-Dense（Qwen3.5-2B/4B/9B）"

msgid "## 1 Introduction"
msgstr "## 1 简介"

msgid ""
"Qwen3.5-2B, Qwen3.5-4B, and Qwen3.5-9B are dense hybrid Mamba-Transformer "
"language models in the Qwen3.5 family. They share the same hybrid attention "
"design (GDN + full attention) and are suitable for general-purpose text "
"generation tasks such as dialogue, content creation, and code generation."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3.5-2B、Qwen3.5-4B 和 Qwen3.5-9B 是 Qwen3.5 系列中的稠密混合 Mamba-Transformer "
"语言模型。它们采用相同的混合注意力设计（GDN + 全注意力），适用于对话、内容创作和代码生成等通用文本生成任务。"

msgid ""
"This document describes deployment and verification of these models on "
"**Atlas inference products** and **Atlas 200I Pro**, including environment "
"preparation, Docker installation, single-node online deployment, functional "
"verification, and tuning notes."
msgstr ""
"本文档描述了在 **Atlas 推理产品** 和 **Atlas 200I Pro** 上部署和验证这些模型的方法，包括环境准备、Docker "
"安装、单节点在线部署、功能验证以及调优说明。"

msgid ""
"It is **strongly recommended to use the latest release candidate (rc) "
"version or the latest official version** of `vllm-ascend`. Support for "
"Qwen3.5-2B/4B/9B on Atlas inference products and Atlas 200I Pro starts from "
"`vllm-ascend:v0.23.0rc1`."
msgstr ""
"**强烈建议使用 `vllm-ascend` 的最新候选发布（rc）版本或最新正式版本**。从 `vllm-ascend:v0.23.0rc1` "
"开始，Atlas 推理产品和 Atlas 200I Pro 支持 Qwen3.5-2B/4B/9B。"

