msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: The following configurations are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends on model size, maximum input/output length, and actual device memory.\n"
">\n"
"> **Atlas inference products / Atlas 200I Pro**: Currently only the TP scenario is supported. Prefer **TP=1** on Atlas 200I Pro. On Atlas inference products, **TP=1** and **TP=2** are both supported; choose according to the available devices. Configure `--max-model-len`, `--max-num-seqs`, and `--gpu-memory-utilization` based on the actual device memory; setting them too high may cause OOM."
msgstr ""
"> **注意**：以下配置仅供参考。最佳配置取决于模型大小、最大输入/输出长度以及实际设备内存。\n"
">\n"
"> **Atlas 推理产品 / Atlas 200I Pro**：目前仅支持 TP 场景。在 Atlas 200I Pro 上建议使用 **TP=1**。在 Atlas 推理产品上，**TP=1** 和 **TP=2** 均支持；请根据可用设备选择。根据实际设备内存配置 `--max-model-len`、`--max-num-seqs` 和 `--gpu-memory-utilization`；设置过高可能导致 OOM。"

